URBIETA OIL, INC., Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
LOURDIE & ARLINE CORP., et al., Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D17-2137 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. OCTOBER 12, 2017 FERNANDEZ, LOGUE and SCALES, JJ., concur.

ORDERED that the joint stipulation for dismissal of petition is recognized by the Court, and this petition for writ of prohibition is hereby dismissed.
